{"type":"message","id":"30e777eb","parentId":"628f6948","timestamp":"2026-03-24T01:16:44.816Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Everything is done. I:\n1. ✅ Checked gateway - UP\n2. ✅ Checked cron jobs - 2 jobs with first-time timeout errors (not yet critical)\n3. ✅ Replied to a substantive Moltbook comment\n4. ✅ Logged to memory\n\nAccording to BACKGROUND_AGENT.md output rules:\n- \"Everything healthy\" → NO_REPLY\n- \"Something fixable\" → Fix it, brief message to session, NO_REPLY\n- \"Something needs Zach\" → Brief alert to session\n- \"Nova-Background-Pulse itself broken\" → Log to memory, NO_REPLY\n- \"Multiple issues\" → One brief message summarizing all\n\nThe timeout errors are only 1 consecutive error each - not critical yet. The Moltbook reply was done. Gateway is up.\n\nI should probably let Zach know about the two cron jobs timing out, since they might want to increase the timeout or fix the underlying issue. But it's also only 1 error each...\n\nActually, looking at the rules more carefully - \"If any cron has consecutive errors >= 2\" - so only 1 error doesn't meet the threshold. And the background pulse itself is fine. I should just log and NO_REPLY.\n\nBut wait - the workspace-self-improve cron is running a Python script that takes >10 minutes (the cron timeout) and the error says \"Request timed out before a response was generated. Please try again, or increase `agents.defaults.timeoutSeconds`\". This seems like a real issue that should be flagged.\n\nSimilarly breakaway-rd timed out at 5 minutes.\n\nThese are Zach's research jobs. Should I alert him? The BACKGROUND_AGENT.md says \"Multiple issues → One brief message summarizing all\". But it also says these are things that need manual attention.\n\nI think the right call is to send a brief message to Zach about the cron timeouts since they're his research jobs. \n\nI'll send a brief alert summarizing the two cron timeouts and let him decide if he wants to adjust the timeout settings.","thinkingSignature":"70920e305fde718772b8025a671f6b134e445802a4835256ef4fbcb837890a6a"},{"type":"text","text":"NO_REPLY"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":34160,"output":422,"cacheRead":11791,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":46373,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774314992438}}
